Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph queue worker

Purpose:
  Internal transient worker entry point for running queue jobs.

Usage:
  wikigraph queue worker [--llm <json>]

Notes:
  - Users normally do not run this directly.
  - Queue mutating commands start the worker when needed.
  - Worker job concurrency follows `job` in `wikg://local/config/concurrent`.
  - LLM request concurrency inside jobs follows `request` in `wikg://local/config/concurrent`.
